tr <find> <replace> - Translating characters for quick replacements.
cat filename | tr ' ' '\n' - Converting spaces to newlines.
cat filename | tr ' ' '*' - Replacing spaces with asterisks.
cat filename | tr ' ' '\n' | xargs -l2 - Splitting and grouping words for further processing.
cat myfirst | tr ' ' '\n' | xargs -l3 | tr ' ' '+' | bc - A powerful combination for arithmetic operations.
seq 10 -2 1 - Generating sequences with step increments.
seq 50 -5 10 - Custom sequences with specified start and end points.
seq -w 01 10 - Zero-padded sequences for uniform length.
seq -s - 10 - Sequences separated by custom characters.
seq -s '*' 10 - Creating sequences with asterisk separators.
